---
/**
 * Step 5 — Boot
 * Post-flash next steps: eject, reboot, BIOS boot menu, Secure Boot.
 */
---

<section
  class="step-panel"
  id="step-panel-5"
  role="tabpanel"
  aria-labelledby="step-tab-5"
>
  <h2>You're Ready to Boot!</h2>
  <p class="step-desc">PAI has been written to your USB drive. Follow these steps to start using it.</p>

  <ol class="boot-steps">
    <li>
      <strong>Safely eject the USB drive</strong>
      <p>Use your OS's "Eject" option before unplugging to ensure all data is written.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Plug the USB into your target machine</strong>
      <p>This can be the same computer or a different one.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Enter the boot menu</strong>
      <p>
        Restart and press the boot-menu key during POST. Common keys:
      </p>
      <div class="boot-keys">
        <span class="boot-key"><kbd>F12</kbd> Dell, Lenovo</span>
        <span class="boot-key"><kbd>F9</kbd> HP</span>
        <span class="boot-key"><kbd>F2</kbd> ASUS, Acer</span>
        <span class="boot-key"><kbd>Option</kbd> Mac</span>
        <span class="boot-key"><kbd>Esc</kbd> Some laptops</span>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Select the USB drive</strong>
      <p>Choose the entry labelled "USB" or your drive's brand name.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Disable Secure Boot (if needed)</strong>
      <p>
        If the USB doesn't appear or fails to boot, enter BIOS/UEFI settings and
        disable Secure Boot. PAI uses a signed shim, but some machines need it off.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <div class="success-banner">
    <p>🎉 PAI will auto-login and launch the AI chat interface. No passwords needed.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="step-actions">
    <a href="/install" class="btn btn--secondary">Full install docs →</a>
    <a href="https://docs.pai.direct/first-steps/first-boot-walkthrough" class="btn btn--primary" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
      First boot guide ↗
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .boot-steps {
    list-style: none;
    counter-reset: boot;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .boot-steps li {
    counter-increment: boot;
    position: relative;
    padding: 16px 16px 16px 52px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }
  .boot-steps li::before {
    content: counter(boot);
    position: absolute;
    left: 16px;
    top: 16px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
    color: #38bdf8;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .boot-steps li strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .boot-steps li p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa; }
  .boot-keys {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .boot-key {
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }
  .boot-key kbd {
    font-family: inherit;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #38bdf8;
  }
  .success-banner {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .success-banner p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
</style>
